Homepage: https://cli.halcon.cloud
Description: AI-powered CLI for software development
 Halcon CLI is a multi-model, open-source AI assistant for software
 development. It supports Anthropic Claude, OpenAI GPT, DeepSeek,
 Ollama, and other providers through a unified interface.
 .
 Features:
  - Interactive REPL with full agent loop
  - Multi-provider support (Anthropic, OpenAI, DeepSeek, Ollama)
  - Persistent memory and session management
  - MCP (Model Context Protocol) server integration
  - TUI mode with activity visualization
  - Tool execution with permission controls
